title: World Record Babes | Sal & Chris Present: Hey Babe! | EP 12
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!


This episode the Babes talk Chris had the best tuna melt of his life, weight loss problems, Sal and Chris do some calorie calculations, SNOW DAYS are BRUTES, TruTV told Chris to lose weight for his pilot, Chris teaches Sal a trick on how to order fast food without looking like a fatty, Chris shaved his eyebrows off by accident, snow day stories, snow days are the Super Bowl for kids, Chris is in the hall of fame at his college, Sal was on a basketball team that lost a game 44 to 0, shout out Yolanda Vega, when Sal was a kid he threw a rock at a girl for not giving him a cookie, soda road rage, birds pooping on you, walking on hot coals, how long does it take to count to a million?, the babes find a world record they were born to destory! THE BABES RUN THE GUINNESS BOOK OF WORLD RECORDS!!! YAASSSSS! HEY BABE!


Rate us on iTunes! Follow us on social media @HeyBabePod
